text: I can't speak for Supra, but I think video game music has a special quality -because- of the stories we associate with the tracks. We're experiencing the game while we hear the music, so the emotions get tied up in the music. What a particular song sparks in your memory is half the joy of VGM, I'd say. But supra's music is awesome all on its own too - I've found great tracks from games I've never played from his uploads.
